---
title: Chicken Fajitas with Homemade Guacamole and Pico De Gallo
description: No need to go to a restaurant tonight! Make your own sizzling chicken fajitas with crunchy red bell pepper, soft caramelized onion, and creamy guacamole.
This dish has party written all over it.
